{"tid":1813331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有現階段唔想自殺嘅人，記住咁撚樣做","createTime":"2020-01-06T07:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T12:49:46.000Z","uid":48234,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"83a110ea7dc2e446434e6db1342c6101490549c1","tid":1813331,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T07:59:01.000Z","msg":"每個人搵三個(或以上)朋友<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">1: 來自唔同家庭<br />\n2: 你同呢三個(或以上)朋友之中，隨便抽兩個人都冇親戚/血緣關係(或者有但唔知)</span><br />\n<br />\n寫定不自殺聲明，再加親筆簽名，交俾佢哋保管<br />\n保管不自殺聲明嘅人可以scan入電腦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當你真心想自殺(或者為港捐驅)嘅時候，需要親手寫遺書加親筆簽名俾晒收過不自殺聲明嘅指定朋友<br />\n以證明自己唔係俾蚑那国安殺</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Q: 如何破解国安強迫你簽遺書?<br />\nA: 簽一個<span style=\"color: red;\">同你不自殺聲明完全唔同嘅簽名</span>，朋友見到簽名完全唔對路就會起疑，即刻知道你被自殺</span>"},{"pid":"e4d74bbd4342a2fda4c3291b01456e1e2e91937c","tid":1813331,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T08:00:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f623cc9ad1605e993ce51f38ee1584c6f4562553","tid":1813331,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T08:19:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc62d129023a5276597d7315a58dc5725e10ae26","tid":1813331,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔該人人都要記得做<br />\n老鳳唔信国安起底能力勁到搵到全部朋友</span></span>"},{"pid":"9b7ec5ca0e1a660c5bc4831e87e951dd61d591ad","tid":1813331,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:39:35.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n唔需要每一個朋友都在用同一個軟件聯絡的"},{"pid":"6add5a8aa329f56446ecde38dfbdccf188cdd604","tid":1813331,"uid":66546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2cca9a0aaa949be3392177bd1f7ff0255547d9e","tid":1813331,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco